202988060.Title: Premier 20 in. 2.42 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
202988060.Description: The Premier 20 in. Freestanding Electric Range puts all the features and convenience of a full-size range into a unit that will accommodate even the most intimate of kitchen spaces. All Premier ranges come with an Exclusive Lifetime Warranty on all Top Burner Elements - Your assurance that you are purchasing a top quality product. Equipped with a lift-up cook top and support rod, this range is a cinch to keep clean. Safety features like the Surface Indicator Light, will let you know at a glance if cooktop burners are on. Our "Keep Warm" Thermostat enables you to set your range to 150°, keeping your food warm without continuing to cook until ready to eat and the Fully Insulated Oven comes with 2 Heavy-Duty Oven Racks with 4 Adjustable Positions. Color: White.

311571238.Title: Avanti 20 in. 2.1 cu. ft. Single Oven Electric Range in White
311571238.Description: This Avanti 20 in. Electric Range Comes with a Backsplash and Storage Drawer. It features 4 coil burners, 2.1 cu. ft. capacity, deluxe see-thru glass oven door, oven cavity light, a backsplash and leveling legs. Color: White.

306296819.Title: Hotpoint 20 in. 2.3 cu. ft. Electric Range Oven in White
306296819.Description: GE appliances provide up-to-date technology and exceptional quality to simplify the way you live. With a timeless appearance, this family of appliances is ideal for your family. And, coming from one of the most trusted names in America, you know that this entire selection of appliances is as advanced as it is practical. Color: White.

202694707.Title: Summit Appliance 20 in. 2.46 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
202694707.Description: Summit Appliance offers a wide selection of household ranges with high quality construction at superior value. Our apartment sized line of electric ranges includes the popular WEM1171Q. At just 20 in. wide, this model is perfectly sized to fit into a tight space but has a large oven for family meals. The complete porcelain and steel construction offers long lasting quality and with a three-prong line cord and indicator lights for each coil and oven, the WEM11171Q can be used in HUD applications or nursing homes. Color: White.

309297432.Title: PREMIUM 20 in. 2.2 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
309297432.Description: PREMIUM's 20 in. 2.2 cu. ft. Electric Range in White is the perfect appliance for your apartment, condo or office kitchen. Just as in larger units there is an in-door window and oven light to allow users to check on food while it is cooking, 2 adjustable wire racks, a broiler tray and grid included, and a handy removable storage drawer. With its small footprint, it conserves space while providing all the functionality you need to cook healthy meals at home.
